{
  "stem": "24346.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Tschenstochova-- ?] in German, Tschenstochau.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we walked on foot to a factory, which we later found out was an ammunition factory.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It produced mostly bullets for rifles.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the beginning, I had no trade, you know, being a mechanic or a machinist, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was, in the beginning, sweeping the floors from the scrapings, whatever got dirty.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the machines, let's say, cut the bullets to a certain size.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When the bullets were not filled with powder yet-- I don't know, I forgot what [? it was. ?] [NON-ENGLISH]-- in German, it's [NON-ENGLISH] and [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The [NON-ENGLISH] is the one that you put the powder in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The [NON-ENGLISH] [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the machines were automatic, and they cut off and used the fall-off material, and used to sweep that together, put it together.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They took it away, melted it and became again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In barracks.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We know that these were horse stables before the war.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Horse stables, and they converted them into barracks to live.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They put up barracks-- it was like one bed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they had the straw inserted in material.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And everybody had one of these.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it was one through the whole barrack.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Quite a few hundred people in the barrack.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What I brought.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was the lucky thing, that I brought a backpack from the ghetto with clothes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were allowed to take clothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That, that, this clothing-- not all of it, part of it-- I put on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't know for sure whether they'll make us part with the backpack or not.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As a precautionary measure, I remember, I put on three pairs of pants, three shirts, other things.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In fact, the fact was, they took away the backpacks from us.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
